---
import Head from '../../components/Head.astro';
import '../../styles/fonts.css';
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<Head
			title="Pascale Richard — Ensemble pour NY 2026"
			description="Candidate Renaissance pour les Français de New York, New Jersey et Connecticut. Journaliste, élue, engagée depuis 2016."
			path="/v/10"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<!-- ═══ HERO — navy → deep blue ═══ -->
		<section class="hero">
			<nav>
				<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_logo-complet_blanc.png" alt="Renaissance" class="nav-logo" />
			</nav>

			<div class="hero-inner">
				<div class="portrait-wrapper">
					<div class="portrait-ring">
						<img src="/assets/images/pascale.jpg" alt="Pascale Richard" class="portrait" />
					</div>
				</div>
				<h1>Pascale Richard</h1>
				<p class="role">Conseillère des Français de l'étranger</p>
				<div class="geo">
					<span>New York</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>New Jersey</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>Connecticut</span>
				</div>

				<div class="gradient-divider"></div>

				<p class="quote">« Le plus satisfaisant est d'aider mes concitoyens. Conseiller des Français de l'étranger est une fonction méconnue, mais les conseillers font un travail important. »</p>

				<ul class="facts">
					<li><strong>25+ ans</strong> à New York</li>
					<li><strong>Engagée</strong> depuis 2016</li>
					<li><strong>Élue</strong> en 2021</li>
					<li><strong>Suppléante</strong> de R. Lescure</li>
				</ul>

				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta animated-gradient-btn">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ PRIORITIES — deep blue → blue-purple ═══ -->
		<section class="priorities">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label">Engagements</p>
				<h2>Trois priorités pour notre communauté</h2>
				<div class="priority-grid">
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-number">01</div>
						<h3>Solidarité</h3>
						<p>Accompagner les Français en difficulté aux États-Unis — personnes âgées isolées, malades, familles touchées par la vie chère. Orienter chacun vers les bons interlocuteurs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-number">02</div>
						<h3>Lien &amp; événements</h3>
						<p>Soutenir les associations et événements qui créent du lien — de Bastille Day aux salons de l'éducation bilingue — et rassembler les Français de toute la circonscription.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-number">03</div>
						<h3>Services numériques</h3>
						<p>Accompagner la mise en place de France Consulaire et le vote par Internet. Tenir les Français informés, simplifier les démarches administratives à distance.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ QUOTE BAND — purple zone ═══ -->
		<section class="quote-band">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="gradient-divider"></div>
				<blockquote>
					« Il y a une résilience des gens qui n'attendent pas tout de leur gouvernement. C'est notre relation à l'État qui doit évoluer. »
				</blockquote>
				<div class="gradient-divider"></div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ TIMELINE — purple → red ═══ -->
		<section class="parcours">
			<div class="container narrow">
				<p class="section-label">Parcours</p>
				<h2>D'une carrière dans les médias à l'engagement politique</h2>
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">Années 2000</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Installation à New York</h4>
							<p>Carrière de journaliste. Rédactrice en chef de France Amérique. Directrice des événements culturels au Lycée Français de New York.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2016</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Engagement avec En Marche</h4>
							<p>S'engage dès la première heure avec le mouvement d'Emmanuel Macron. Campagne aux côtés de Roland Lescure pour l'Amérique du Nord.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2017</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Suppléante du député Lescure</h4>
							<p>Suppléante pendant la première mandature du député de la 1ère circonscription des Français établis hors de France.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2021</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Élue conseillère des Français de l'étranger</h4>
							<p>Tête de liste En Marche pour NY, NJ, CT et les Bermudes. Élue à l'Assemblée des Français de l'étranger, commission développement durable.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item current">
						<span class="tl-year">2026</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Candidate aux législatives</h4>
							<p>Candidate Renaissance aux élections législatives pour représenter les Français de la circonscription tri-state.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ EVENTS — warm red zone ═══ -->
		<section class="events">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label">Événements</p>
				<h2>Rencontrons-nous</h2>
				<div class="events-placeholder">
					<p class="coming-soon">À venir</p>
					<p class="events-sub">Le calendrier des événements et rencontres sera bientôt disponible. Suivez-nous sur Instagram pour rester informé.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ CTA BOTTOM — red → navy loop ═══ -->
		<section class="cta-bottom">
			<div class="container">
				<h2>Rejoignez le mouvement</h2>
				<p class="cta-sub">Ensemble, construisons l'avenir de notre communauté française aux États-Unis.</p>
				<div class="buttons">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta animated-gradient-btn">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ FOOTER — dark to near-black ═══ -->
		<footer>
			<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_monogramme_blanc.png" alt="Renaissance" class="footer-logo" />
			<p>&copy; 2026 Pascale Richard &mdash; Ensemble pour NY 2026</p>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	/* ─── CUSTOM PROPERTIES ─── */
	:root {
		--navy: #001B6E;
		--blue: #002395;
		--purple: #4A1B7A;
		--red: #ED2939;
		--orange: #FF6B35;
		--white: #FFFFFF;
	}

	* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

	html {
		font-family: 'Maax', system-ui, sans-serif;
		color: var(--white);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
		font-size: 16px;
	}

	body {
		background: #000;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.container.narrow {
		max-width: 720px;
	}

	/* ─── GRADIENT DIVIDER ─── */
	.gradient-divider {
		width: 80px;
		height: 3px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--purple), var(--red), var(--orange));
	}

	/* ─── ANIMATED GRADIENT BUTTON ─── */
	.animated-gradient-btn {
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--orange), var(--purple), var(--red));
		background-size: 300% 100%;
		animation: gradientShift 4s ease infinite;
		border: none;
	}

	.animated-gradient-btn:hover {
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--orange), var(--purple), var(--red));
		background-size: 300% 100%;
		animation: gradientShift 2s ease infinite;
		filter: brightness(1.15);
	}

	@keyframes gradientShift {
		0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
		50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
		100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
	}

	/* ─── ROTATING GRADIENT RING ─── */
	@keyframes ringRotate {
		0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
		100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   HERO — navy → deep blue
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	.hero {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #000D35 0%, var(--navy) 30%, var(--blue) 100%);
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
	}

	nav {
		padding: 2rem 2rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.nav-logo {
		height: 22px;
		opacity: 0.75;
	}

	.hero-inner {
		max-width: 640px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem;
	}

	/* ─── PORTRAIT WITH ANIMATED RING ─── */
	.portrait-wrapper {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.portrait-ring {
		position: relative;
		width: 164px;
		height: 164px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.portrait-ring::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: conic-gradient(
			var(--navy),
			var(--blue),
			var(--purple),
			var(--red),
			var(--orange),
			var(--red),
			var(--purple),
			var(--blue),
			var(--navy)
		);
		animation: ringRotate 6s linear infinite;
	}

	.portrait-ring::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 4px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--navy);
	}

	.portrait {
		width: 152px;
		height: 152px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.08;
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--white) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.85) 50%, var(--white) 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.role {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
	}

	.geo {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
	}

	.dot {
		width: 5px;
		height: 5px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), var(--orange));
	}

	.hero .gradient-divider {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.hero .quote {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		max-width: 500px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.facts {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.facts li {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
	}

	.facts strong {
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), var(--red));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.hero .buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	/* ─── SHARED BUTTON STYLES ─── */
	.cta {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2.25rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.25s;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta.ghost {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--white);
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.cta.ghost:hover {
		border-color: var(--white);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   PRIORITIES — deep blue → blue-purple
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	.priorities {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--blue) 0%, #1A1478 50%, var(--purple) 100%);
		padding: 6rem 0;
	}

	.section-label {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), var(--red));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.priorities h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.priority-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.75rem;
	}

	.priority-card {
		position: relative;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
		backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	/* Gradient border via pseudo-element */
	.priority-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		border-radius: 10px;
		padding: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple), var(--red), var(--orange));
		-webkit-mask:
			linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,
			linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
		-webkit-mask-composite: xor;
		mask-composite: exclude;
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	.card-number {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--orange));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.priority-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.1875rem;
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.priority-card p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   QUOTE BAND — purple zone
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	.quote-band {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--purple) 0%, #5A2088 50%, var(--purple) 100%);
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.quote-band .gradient-divider {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.quote-band blockquote {
		max-width: 640px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
		font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.375rem);
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   TIMELINE — purple → red
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	.parcours {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--purple) 0%, #6B1A50 40%, #8B1A35 70%, var(--red) 100%);
	}

	.parcours h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 3.5rem;
	}

	/* Gradient timeline line */
	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0.5625rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		bottom: 0.375rem;
		width: 2px;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--purple), var(--red), var(--orange));
	}

	.tl-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 2.75rem;
	}

	.tl-item:last-child {
		padding-bottom: 0;
	}

	.tl-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -3.5rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		width: 13px;
		height: 13px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
		border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		transform: translateX(calc(0.5625rem - 50% + 1px));
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.tl-item.current::before {
		background: var(--orange);
		border-color: var(--orange);
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
	}

	.tl-year {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), #FFB088);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.tl-content h4 {
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.tl-content p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   EVENTS — warm red zone
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	.events {
		padding: 6rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--red) 0%, #C4212F 50%, #A01A28 100%);
	}

	.events h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		color: var(--white);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.events-placeholder {
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		max-width: 560px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--white);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.events-sub {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		max-width: 400px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   CTA BOTTOM — red → navy (loops back)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	.cta-bottom {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #A01A28 0%, #5A1040 30%, var(--purple) 50%, var(--navy) 100%);
		padding: 6rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta-bottom h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta-sub {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.cta-bottom .buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   FOOTER — subtle gradient to near-black
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	footer {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--navy) 0%, #000820 100%);
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.footer-logo {
		height: 36px;
		width: auto;
		opacity: 0.45;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════
	   RESPONSIVE
	   ═══════════════════════════════════ */
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.priority-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			max-width: 480px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.hero-inner {
			padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
		}

		.portrait-ring {
			width: 140px;
			height: 140px;
		}

		.portrait {
			width: 128px;
			height: 128px;
		}

		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}

		.role {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.geo {
